{"tid":275808,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[分享] 分析各大酒店品牌優惠及會籍討論","createTime":"2017-06-08T10:20:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-10T11:49:25.000Z","uid":16376,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"66f270b030dc328e5fcf84e7ab3a0bf9b347125f","tid":275808,"uid":16376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T10:20:32.000Z","msg":"小弟都係岩岩接觸酒店會籍，平時都係儲下里數多，希望各位高手都可以一齊討論下，研究點樣可以用會籍拎到更高級享受既入住。<br />\n以下有D資料未必岩曬，或者酒店條款改左，大家訂房個陣都最好打去cs問一問先<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">A.酒店品牌</span><br />\n<br />\n其實全球見到好多酒店既品牌，但係其實都係幾個集團旗下，比較出名既有:<br />\n<br />\n1.\tSPG<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/yd6ig0b8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fyd6ig0b8&h=a70c49e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2.\tMarriot Rewards<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/fn7vprui\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Ffn7vprui&h=7e58f495&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n3.\tIHG<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/q2wm3ctp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fq2wm3ctp&h=08e6e21e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n4.\tHilton<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/pejqgomw\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fpejqgomw&h=b444e138&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n5.\tLe Club Accor<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/ye1mloz0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fye1mloz0&h=c21e5b9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n6.\tHyatt<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/s2384nig\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fs2384nig&h=e2b5e533&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">*Marriot收購左SPG，所以佢地而家D會籍都可以通用。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">SPG</span></span><br />\n<br />\n因為自己呢幾日都睇左SPG Membership，不如就係呢到講起，SPG旗下既酒店大家都唔陌生，比較出名既有 Sheraton, W Hotel, Westin<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/oezydcbg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Foezydcbg&h=620c9259&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而SPG Member可以分做三個等級:<br />\n優先禮遇顧客   <br />\n黃金優先禮遇顧客   每年 10 次住宿/25 晚<br />\n白金優先禮遇顧客   每年 25 次住宿/50 晚<br />\n<br />\n講左咁耐，不如從優惠入手，而家最Hot又最多野玩既就有一夜升金，65折買分。其他就有買5送1等等。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>一夜升金</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"http://www.spg-asiapacific.com/worldmastercardgold/tw/#.WTj-teuGOM8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.spg-asiapacific.com%2Fworldmastercardgold%2Ftw%2F%23.WTj-teuGOM8&d=9QbquKIHcXcapsTpPLjncvM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=c85c52a9\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.spg-asiapacific.com/worldmastercardgold/tw/#.WTj-teuGOM8</a></span><br />\n如果你手持World Master卡就恭喜你，你可以參加呢個活動，即係用World Master Card付款入住Spg旗下酒店一晚(有部分酒店唔包)，就可以升做金卡會員一年。<br />\n金卡會員權利如下:<br />\n入住時客房升等<br />\n下午 4 時延遲退房優惠<br />\n每一美元消費，可累積 Starpoints&reg; 3 點，比一般會員積點多 50%。<br />\n可兌換無限制免費住宿、SPG 機票、現金回饋及積點、SPG MomentsSM，以及 SPG 特約商店的暢銷商品。<br />\n<br />\n大家見到客房升等應該好興奮，但唔好有任何期望，其實最實用都係延遲退房。<br />\n同埋上面提過Marriot收購左SPG，所以SPG金卡係可以轉做Marriot金卡，最好就係可以入Lounge。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>65折買分</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"https://buy.points.com/marketing/spg/landing_page/ \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbuy.points.com%2Fmarketing%2Fspg%2Flanding_page%2F%20&d=9QbquKIHcXcapsTpPLjncvM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=9e4e4a1f\" target=\"_blank\">https://buy.points.com/marketing/spg/landing_page/ </a></span><br />\n<br />\n呢個活動係限期(2017/6/30前)，會員可以用65折既優惠去買SPG分。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><em>1.\t換酒店住宿</em></span><br />\n<br />\n咁D分有咩用，緊係可以換酒店，以下就List左常見既酒店，要用幾多分換(我用7月中入住做參考)<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/n9t3zylr\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fn9t3zylr&h=3d6ef14a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSheraton Miyako Hotel Osaka = 10000 Starpoint<br />\n澳門喜來登金沙城中心大酒店 = 10000 Starpoint<br />\n曼谷 W 酒店 (W Bangkok) = 10000 Starpoint<br />\n大阪瑞吉酒店 = 20000 Starpoint<br />\n<br />\n以大阪瑞吉酒店做例子，如果我係官網直接訂價錢會係(可更改日期及取消)<br />\n<br />\n1晚 : 每間客房 / 晚 + 費用與稅金 = JPY 40,986 = HKD 2897<br />\n20000 Starpoint = USD455 = 3594<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><em>2.\t轉為里數</em></span><br />\n<br />\n呢個時候你可能會話，直接用錢訂仲抵啦，點解要買分<br />\n因為有時用分換旺季/套房真係抵好多好多，所以可以自己試下邊D抵再買。<br />\n<br />\n除此之外，Starpoint仲可以換里數，例如:達美，Emirates，東方航空，英航Avios<br />\n睇過好多Blog，好多人都會換Avios，換率為1:1(一次性換20000再送5000)<br />\nAvios係寰宇一家既，所以成個家族既航空都可以換，例如國泰航空、卡塔爾航空、日本航空。<br />\n又到例子時間<br />\n因為換20000送5000 ，而Avios去日本來回要20000里，2個人計就要40000<br />\n即係我買35000 Starpoint就得<br />\n35000 Starpoint = USD682.5 = HKD5391<br />\n<br />\n而CX官網就要<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/mgztbh5v\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fmgztbh5v&h=ce1108ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁當然日子出發時間唔同，個價都可以差好遠，不過大多數都係用分抵D，如果巴打們真係訂，最好打去Hotline問清楚，以免有D咩誤會用唔到。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><em>3.\t換門票及特別經歷</em></span><br />\n另外仲可以用黎換球賽，演唱會門票加特別經歷<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">[url] https://auction.starw<a href=\"https://auction.starwoodhotels.com/moments/passion/culinaryoodhotels.com/moments/passion/culinary\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fauction.starwoodhotels.com%2Fmoments%2Fpassion%2Fculinaryoodhotels.com%2Fmoments%2Fpassion%2Fculinary&d=9QbquKIHcXcapsTpPLjncvM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=72b0312f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://auction.starwoodhotels.com/moments/passion/culinaryoodhotels.com/moments/passion/culinary</a> [/url]</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實小弟都係岩岩接觸呢D酒店會員，目的係引多D連登高手出黎，教下大家點玩最抵。<br />\n聽日就講下Marriot Rewards! 大家有咩唔明都可以問下，希望我或者其他高手可以答到你問題。"},{"pid":"6ba87e7aa9074cb2ea39999693cad9d7d27a1497","tid":275808,"uid":16376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T10:49:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"879dcdde408f6571e2ac57cc79365db8501213c6","tid":275808,"uid":27991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T10:52:20.000Z","msg":"1&amp;2 基本上係同一個集團<br />\n我都有join<br />\n<br />\nSPG 某部分酒店房可以用iPhone 開門"},{"pid":"8e21fb76c4d8607ad3a138bea4ec47a8fcfe753d","tid":275808,"uid":16376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T10:57:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1&amp;2 基本上係同一個集團<br />\n我都有join<br />\n<br />\nSPG 某部分酒店房可以用iPhone 開門</blockquote><br />\nKeyless <br />\n巴打玩到咩level<br />\n基本上有spg就有marriot"},{"pid":"0c458c706dda80323603fc1ed4a4d463d0efcc6a","tid":275808,"uid":16376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T11:06:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a389b71ea007e59528e40a457dbd0d0a90858a40","tid":275808,"uid":16376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T11:51:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5087f93d13d455e3d600c4eb6e7397a6bcf10aa7","tid":275808,"uid":16376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T11:55:49.000Z","msg":"咁都有負評"},{"pid":"0ef02d6a06d7310fa69c5a78098397e8ab3395f4","tid":275808,"uid":16376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T12:59:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edaddcfcbdf41a99fcdcd83c7b7630d2ab520ad6","tid":275808,"uid":18948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T13:04:48.000Z","msg":"淨係不斷見到啲鬼佬有分用唔到𨳒曬鬼"},{"pid":"2a721326a9493fd99d65c51d10f19f6cf7c11890","tid":275808,"uid":18948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T13:05:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.consumeraffairs.com/travel/hilton_grand_vacations.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.consumeraffairs.com%2Ftravel%2Fhilton_grand_vacations.html&d=9QbquKIHcXcapsTpPLjncvM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=f9301360\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.consumeraffairs.com/travel/hilton_grand_vacations.html</a>"},{"pid":"88cd414abe4f919d2492711730ee0aeb6030b024","tid":275808,"uid":16376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T13:09:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>淨係不斷見到啲鬼佬有分用唔到𨳒曬鬼</blockquote><br />\n其實都會有呢D情況發生,多數係旺季同埋BK熱門酒店又高grade既房<br />\n不過身邊既人又好少試過"},{"pid":"a039919329d1cc30bd958c4eb2cb45e0cc59475b","tid":275808,"uid":16376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T13:15:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36aef616014f8f6a18a9b001d6618b785cb6ab8a","tid":275808,"uid":52006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T13:20:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e0333c29bddc7ee30831148b0ea3423ee1914a2","tid":275808,"uid":16376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T13:22:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d37a65f1fe17bdd51b69eeb68969b7737572c88","tid":275808,"uid":16376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T14:06:10.000Z","msg":"連登無人玩酒店?"},{"pid":"62b5b778009657213200090a2dee207111d20bf3","tid":275808,"uid":16376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T15:29:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e62bdabacd56ad83bdcac2b560bec9320fdddb6","tid":275808,"uid":16376,"li